---
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import EmailForm from '~/components/ui/EmailForm.astro';

const metadata = {
  title: 'Science-led education for aging skin changes',
  ignoreTitleTemplate: true,
};
---

<Layout metadata={metadata}>
  <section class="px-4 sm:px-6 py-14 sm:py-20 mx-auto max-w-6xl">
    <p class="text-sm font-medium text-accent mb-4">Science-led education for skin changes after 60</p>
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-heading max-w-4xl">
      This Is Not About Hygiene. This Is About What Changes in Your Skin After 60.
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-muted max-w-3xl">
      Most people try to fix surface symptoms. But aging skin behaves differently — at a biological level.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-6 text-sm font-medium text-default/90">
      MD, PhD in Biophysics | 30+ Years in Pharmaceutical R&amp;D | Delivery Systems Innovator
    </p>
    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3">
      <a class="btn-primary" href="#guide">Get the Free Guide</a>
      <a class="btn-secondary" href="#education">Start Here</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="px-4 sm:px-6 py-12 mx-auto max-w-6xl border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">A Different Way to Think About Skin</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-muted max-w-3xl">
      Most cosmetic advice treats skin like a surface. But skin is not passive. It is a dynamic biological system that
      changes with age.
    </p>
    <ul class="mt-6 space-y-2 text-default list-disc pl-5">
      <li>This is not a cleanliness issue</li>
      <li>This is not about “stronger products”</li>
      <li>This is about how biology shifts over time</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="px-4 sm:px-6 py-12 mx-auto max-w-6xl">
    <h2 class="sr-only">Entry points</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 p-6 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Understand What’s Happening</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-muted">Articles and education for understanding how skin changes with age.</p>
        <a class="mt-5 inline-flex font-medium text-primary hover:text-secondary" href="#insights">Start Learning →</a>
      </article>
      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 p-6 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Find What Actually Works</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-muted">Future solutions designed around aging skin behavior.</p>
        <a class="mt-5 inline-flex font-medium text-primary hover:text-secondary" href="#early-access"
          >See the Approach →</a
        >
      </article>
      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 p-6 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Follow a Structured Approach</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-muted">A guided way to understand changes, options, and next steps.</p>
        <a class="mt-5 inline-flex font-medium text-primary hover:text-secondary" href="#guide">Explore the System →</a>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="px-4 sm:px-6 py-12 mx-auto max-w-6xl border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">You may be doing everything right…</h2>
    <ul class="mt-5 space-y-2 list-disc pl-5">
      <li>You shower regularly</li>
      <li>You use quality products</li>
      <li>You follow hygiene routines</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mt-6 font-semibold">And yet…</p>
    <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 list-disc pl-5">
      <li>Your skin feels different</li>
      <li>Products stop working</li>
      <li>Something changes — quietly</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mt-6 text-lg font-medium">Most people never realize why.</p>
  </section>

  <section id="education" class="px-4 sm:px-6 py-12 mx-auto max-w-6xl">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-start">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">What Actually Changes With Age</h2>
        <ul class="mt-5 space-y-2 text-default list-disc pl-5">
          <li>Lipid composition shifts</li>
          <li>Microbial environment changes</li>
          <li>Compound formation changes, including age-related scent compounds such as 2-nonenal</li>
          <li>Barrier function declines</li>
        </ul>
        <a class="mt-6 inline-flex font-medium text-primary hover:text-secondary" href="#guide"
          >Get the full explanation in the free guide →</a
        >
      </div>
      <aside
        class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 p-5 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-slate-900"
        aria-label="Skin system layers"
      >
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Skin System Layers (Simplified)</h3>
        <ol class="mt-4 space-y-3">
          <li class="rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 px-4 py-3 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
            Surface
          </li>
          <li class="rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 px-4 py-3 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
            Lipid layer
          </li>
          <li class="rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 px-4 py-3 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
            Microbial environment
          </li>
          <li class="rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 px-4 py-3 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
            Barrier function
          </li>
        </ol>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="guide" class="px-4 sm:px-6 py-12 mx-auto max-w-6xl border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">The Senior’s Guide to Aging Skin &amp; Body Odor</h2>
    <ul class="mt-5 space-y-2 list-disc pl-5">
      <li>Why skin behaves differently after 60</li>
      <li>What most products ignore</li>
      <li>The truth about age-related scent changes</li>
      <li>What actually helps — and what doesn’t</li>
    </ul>
    <EmailForm
      formName="free-guide"
      thankYouKey="free-guide"
      thankYouMessage="Thanks — your free guide request was received. Check your inbox for the next step."
      button="Download Free Guide"
      emailId="guide-email"
      ariaLabel="Free guide signup form"
      class="mt-8 max-w-xl"
    />
  </section>

  <section class="px-4 sm:px-6 py-12 mx-auto max-w-6xl">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">A Different Kind of Solution</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-muted">If the system has changed, then the solution must change too.</p>
    <ul class="mt-5 space-y-2 list-disc pl-5">
      <li>Works with biological function</li>
      <li>Designed for aging skin behavior</li>
      <li>Built on delivery system science</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section id="early-access" class="px-4 sm:px-6 py-12 mx-auto max-w-6xl border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">Currently in Development</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-lg font-medium">Deodorant cream for aging-related odor.</p>
    <p class="mt-3 text-muted max-w-3xl">
      Not a stronger deodorant. A different approach to how scent forms in aging skin.
    </p>
    <a class="btn-primary mt-6" href="#guide">Join Early Access List</a>
  </section>

  <section class="px-4 sm:px-6 py-12 mx-auto max-w-6xl">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">Built on Medical &amp; Scientific Systems Thinking</h2>
    <ul class="mt-5 space-y-2 list-disc pl-5">
      <li>MD + PhD in Biophysics</li>
      <li>30+ years in pharmaceutical R&amp;D</li>
      <li>Developed patented delivery systems</li>
      <li>Experience from concept → clinical → product</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mt-5 text-sm text-muted">Educational content only. Not medical advice.</p>
  </section>

  <section id="insights" class="px-4 sm:px-6 py-12 mx-auto max-w-6xl border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">Start With These Insights</h2>
    <div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
      {
        [
          'Why Body Odor Changes After 60',
          'What Is 2-Nonenal — And Why It Matters',
          'Why ‘Stronger’ Products Often Fail',
          'The Truth About Anti-Aging Claims',
          'What Your Skin Is Actually Doing Now',
        ].map((title) => (
          <article class="rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 p-4 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900">
            <h3 class="font-semibold">{title}</h3>
          </article>
        ))
      }
    </div>
    <a class="mt-6 inline-flex font-medium text-primary hover:text-secondary" href="/blog">Read More Insights →</a>
  </section>

  <section id="quiz" class="px-4 sm:px-6 py-12 mx-auto max-w-6xl">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">What Is Your Skin Trying to Tell You?</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-muted max-w-3xl">
      Take a short quiz to identify which changes may be most relevant to you. Results will require email.
    </p>
    <a class="btn-secondary mt-6" href="#guide">Take the 2-Minute Quiz</a>
  </section>

  <section class="px-4 sm:px-6 py-12 mx-auto max-w-6xl border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">What People Notice First</h2>
    <div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
      <article class="rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 p-5 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900">
        <p>“A more confident daily routine.”</p>
      </article>
      <article class="rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 p-5 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900">
        <p>“A cleaner-feeling approach.”</p>
      </article>
      <article class="rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 p-5 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900">
        <p>“A subtle but meaningful change.”</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="px-4 sm:px-6 py-12 mx-auto max-w-6xl">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">Understand Your Skin — Step by Step</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-muted">Weekly insights from Dr. Lurié.</p>
    <EmailForm
      formName="newsletter"
      thankYouKey="newsletter"
      thankYouMessage="Thanks for joining. Watch your inbox for weekly Dr. Lurié insights."
      button="Join the Newsletter"
      emailId="newsletter-email"
      ariaLabel="Newsletter signup form"
      class="mt-6 max-w-xl"
    />
  </section>

  <section class="px-4 sm:px-6 py-14 mx-auto max-w-6xl border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">
    <h2 class="sr-only">Final close</h2>
    <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-medium max-w-4xl">
      Most people try to fix the surface. But the system has already changed. Once you understand that, everything else
      becomes clearer.
    </p>
    <a class="btn-primary mt-8" href="#guide">Get the Free Guide</a>
  </section>
</Layout>
